{"tid":1239213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲 ：香港人去G-20向特朗普請願，是做什麼呢？","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:05:18.000Z","uid":131157,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"451807483cd34843f0ac4f14bb5682e0afac5c96","tid":1239213,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港人去G-20向特朗普請願，是做什麼呢？是香港人民向國際社會發出求救訊號（SOS）。<br />\n香港這艘船發出求救訊號，有無人來救援呢？看看囉。香港這艘船，上面有許多珍寶和各種人才，守船的香港人要向外求援，而這艘船也不是那麼快沉沒，現在是提早發出求援訊號，就可以慢慢等待外國援手。寶船發出SOS，好似美女掀起紗裙，各國都會來搶救。G-20是有20個全球頂峰國家在場看到的啊！而且剛好遇上中美貿易談判在此舉行。<br />\n其實歐盟和美國已經伸出援手，但他們要顧忌香港的實然主權，隔開衣服，伸手不及肉體。現在，擁有主權的香港人民正式發出求救訊號，外國師出有名，援手就可以伸得很長很入。摸到重點，高潮了。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;陳雲鹹濕論政<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59f53c850f3b76e9203d29304aa3bd3077fd415","tid":1239213,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4d2084378a5e928208e14a4818c52982fcf9e4","tid":1239213,"uid":23407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3cc7a3ff74e8b138d3fef0b6141e51a4e974fe","tid":1239213,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"國師話ok就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2efcd9b24d68e15158c344bedbcb33704f4f710","tid":1239213,